11:
Trust in Yahweh and in his power;
\q2 continually seek to get help from him.
\q1

15:
He never forgets the covenants that he has made;
\q2 he made a promise that will last for a thousand generations.
\q1

19:
He said that to them when there were only a few of them,
\q2 a tiny group of people who were living in that land like strangers;
\q1

24:
Tell among the nations that he is great;
\q2 tell all the people groups the marvelous things that he has done.
\q1

32:
The oceans and all the creatures that are in the oceans should shout;
\q2 the fields and everything that is in them should rejoice.
\q1
